thread.title: Jonny
thread.title_full: Pixels Logo Design reviewed by Jonny

author: Jonny
title: Jonny
text:
So far all my interactions with Pixels Logo Design have been excellent. The on line chat facility has answered all my questions or rectified any issues really quickly.
If you're looking for good quality service at a sensible price - look no further.
Logo supplied in every file format you could need and in 2 colours.
If you want sub 24hr turnaround times then pay a lot more and look elsewhere but I doubt you'll get a better quality product.
